Statistical evaluation of the data was carried out with the software package SAS for Windows (Version 9.3, SAS Institute, Cary, NC). A mixed models approach (procedure PROC MIXED) was used, considering the effects of treatment factors “diet type” (BD or GD), “diet” (BD, GD6, or GD7), “enzyme” (0, phytase, phytase/xylanase), and interaction between these factors, as fixed and “block” effects as random. The model can be described by the following equation:
